text.section:
The purpose of this Fund is:
Dissemination of information pertaining to nongame wildlife species and threatened and endangered species conservation, management, and values;
Scientific investigation and survey of nongame wildlife species and threatened and endangered species for better protection and conservation;
Propagation, distribution, protection, and restoration of nongame wildlife species and threatened and endangered species;
Research and management of nongame wildlife species and threatened and endangered species;
Development of habitats for nongame wildlife species and threatened and endangered species;
Acquisition of habitats for nongame wildlife species and threatened and endangered species; and
Matching of funds available to the Department under federal programs for projects and activities authorized under this section.
